a still of 4387 m/s delta-v and I am on Orbit what should I do 

It met the kraken and blew up for some reason

So my Rocket; UKA mk1 (United Kerbal Association )

it has 77 parts, 9 stages and 6247 total of DeltaV

Presuming you're in LKO you could do a munar flyby, Mimnus flyby or landing, or even if your good maybe a Duna flyby. ( if your completely exploded though you're screwed ) 

Edited April 4, 2016 by Dfthu
That much dV you can do a flyby of pretty much anything, and Land on most moons plus Dres or eeloo. Practice some slingshot manouvers!  Get a flyby of Eve and use it to sling you to Moho
Assuming it's still working, you can try some stuff here. Also, why is this in challenges and mission ideas? Just wondering.
